aliments
Ottawa, ON, Canada, K1A 0Y9
<kim.klotins@inspection.gc.ca>

[I appreciate Dr Klotins's comment correcting my misunderstanding. It
was a misinterpretation of the wording of a news report that lead to
my incorrect understanding. My apology is extended to our readers and
especially to Canada. Thank for your sharp eyes and your effort to
keep our reporting accurate. - Mod.TG]
